				<td colspan="2"><span>From looking at Lucy, Divine Intervention is a cleric buff that lasts for 10 minutes.
<br />

<br />
If you die, there's some chance that if you have this buff, you will be restored to full health, and the chances are raised by the recipient of the buff's charisma, not the caster's.
<br />

<br />
So it's kind of like how Dex affects weapon procs.  This one is a &quot;death proc&quot; <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />
</span></td>
