				<td colspan="2"><span>DI is incidental and generally not a critical component on tier 1 bosses in POP.  Bertox quads for around 1200-1500 sometimes.  Rydda'Dar can quad for 2060 X4 plus a DD.  If you head to GoD and try the Weapon Master, he can quad for 3000+.  There is no tank in the game who can take that kind of beating if the mob gets lucky and quads for full.  It really depends on the level of bosses you're fighting.  There are encounters in the Elementals where DI is simply a necessity.  It will be cast on the tank and restored every time it goes off.  I've heard stories of elemental god fights where DI goes off half a dozen times during the course of the fight.  It is a standard tactic once you reach tier 2/3 POP bosses.</span></td>
