Side note to Bards in MT group that melee. If you get agro and are on ramp you might be hurting the MT group overall because your pulling hp away from group when the time comes to use balance hp. Your also not helping cleric in group who has to break from their chain to heal you. MT group is like &quot;The Place to Be&quot; in most guilds because the best o the best usually in it. But ultimatly its as boring as AE marr &amp; 32 Clarity songs groups were. You not losing hp is just as important as not dropping songs.
