				<td colspan="2"><span>Hrm...in higher end guilds I imagine the agi from VoV might be redundant, since the tanks probably would be capped, though that's one of the harder stats to max.
<br />

<br />
From what I can tell, Guardian won't stack with VoV, but Harmonic stacks with everything.  So if MR is more important (and the tank somehow is not capped with Psalm), go with Guardian, but if AC/agi is more important, go with VoV.  I'm guessing that the Agi/AC components of VoV might not stack with the chanter haste buff, but no info on that.
<br />

<br />
Course you run into the &gt;3 song lag issue on raids...you'd need 2 bards to reliably do Niv's, Psalm, Cha, and Guardian or VoV.  </span></td>
